<div class="inner" id="msg_1033146"><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size"><strong>【Taldor, Echoes of Glory】</strong></span><br><br><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size"><strong>谨慎躲藏（Carefully Hidden）</strong></span><br>出自《塔尔多，荣光余荡之地 pg. 14》<br>类型：种族<br>需求：人类——卡拉什人<br>现代的塔尔多对卡拉什人并不友好。做为一名不受欢迎的异族分子，你掌握了神奇的窍门来避免被察觉到。你的意志检定获得+1背景加值，对抗预言系效果的豁免检定获得+2背景加值。<br><a href="http://www.goddessfantasy.net/bbs/index.php?topic=83830.msg808169#msg808169" class="bbc_link new_win" target="_blank">http://www.goddessfantasy.net/bbs/index.php?topic=83830.msg808169#msg808169</a><br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i>原文</i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">Carefully Hidden<br>Source Taldor, Echoes of Glory pg. 14<br>Category Race<br>Requirement(s) Human - Keleshite<br>Modern Taldor is not kind to Keleshites. Your life as a member of an unpopular ethnic group has given you an uncanny knack for avoiding detection. You gain a +1 trait bonus to Will saves and a +2 trait bonus to saving throws versus divination effects.</div></div></div><br><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size"><strong>业余艺术家（Dilettante Artist）</strong></span><br>出自《Taldor, Echoes of Glory pg. 14》<br>类型：种族<br>需求：精灵<br>艺术对你来说就是一种社交途径，你通过艺术来影响并打动上流社会。你在1种表演检定和交涉检定获得+1背景加值。其中1个技能（由你选择）将会被视为你的本职技能。<br><div style