gory Religion<br>Requirement(s) Iomedae<br>From an early age, you were trained by militaristic order of clerics. You are devoted both to the teachings of Iomadae and to spreading those teachings by force. Your divine spells gain a +1 trait bonus to melee weapon damage.</div></div></div></div>
