"><div style="display: none;">River Rat<br>Source Ultimate Campaign pg. 63, Taldor, Echoes of Glory pg. 13, Advanced Player&#039;s Guide pg. 1<br>Category Region<br>Requirement(s) Marsh or River<br>You learned to swim right after you learned to walk. When you were a youth, a gang of river pirates put you to work swimming in nighttime rivers and canals with a dagger between your teeth so you could sever the anchor ropes of merchant vessels. You gain a +1 trait bonus on damage rolls with a dagger and a +1 trait bonus on Swim checks. Swim is always a class skill for you.</div></div></div><br><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size"><strong>乐天派（Patient Optimist）</strong></span><br>出自《Ultimate Campaign pg. 64, Cheliax, Empire of Devils pg. 19, Advanced Player&#039;s Guide pg. 1》<br>类型：宗教<br>需求：埃拉斯蒂尔<br>你知道一切都会随时间过去，并习惯了再三尝试去说服那些最顽固的信徒。你在影响敌对和不友好生物的交涉检定中获得+2背景加值，如果该次交涉失败还能够重试1次。<br><a href="http://www.goddessfantasy.net/bbs/?topic=60798.msg566149#msg566149" class="bbc_link new_win" target="_blank">http://www.goddessfantasy.net/bbs/?topic=60798.msg566149#msg566149</a><br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i>原文</i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">Patient Optimist<br>Source Ultimate Campaign pg. 64, Cheliax, Empire of Devils pg. 19, Advanced Player&#039;s Guide pg. 1<br>Category Religion<br>Requirement(s) Erastil<br>You know that all things pass in time, and are used to having to repeat arguments multiple times to convince stubborn believers. You gain a +2 trait bonus on Diplomacy checks to inf luence hostile or unfriendly creatures, and if you fail at such an attempt, you may retry it once.</div></div></div><br><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size"><strong>圣战使（Divine Warrior）</strong></span><br>出自《Ultimate Campaign pg. 64, Taldor, Echoes of Glory pg. 14, Advanced Player&#039;s Guide pg. 1》<br>类型：宗教<br>需求：艾奥梅黛<br>你早年曾受训于一所军事修会。你全身心地投入到女神的教义，以及用力量传播教义中去。每当你施放影响任何近战武器的神术时，选择该武器中的1把，它在法术持续时间中在伤害骰获得+1背景加值。<br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">Divine Warrior<br>Source Ultimate Campaign pg. 64, Taldor, Echoes of Glory pg. 14, Advanced Player&#039;s Guide pg. 1<br>Category Religion<br>Requirement(s) Iomedae<br>From an early age, you were trained by a militaristic order of clerics. You are devoted to the teachings of Iomedae and to spreading those teachings by force. Whenever you cast a divine spell that affects any melee weapons, choose one of those weapons; it gains a +1 trait bonus on damage rolls for the duration of the spell.</div></div></div><br><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size"><strong>心御体（Wisdom in the Flesh）</strong></span><br>出自《Ultimate Campaign pg. 64, Legacy of Fire Player&#039;s Guide pg. 9, Advanced Player&#039;s Guide pg. 1》<br>类型：宗教<br>需求：义洛理<br>你对内在完美、力量与速度本质的长时冥思，使你能将精神与思考高度集中，完成那些仅凭肉体无法办到的事情。选择一项基于力量、敏捷或体质的技能。你在使用该技能时，用感知修正取代原本的属性。该技能将视为你的本职技能。<br><a href="http://www.goddessfantasy.net/bbs/?topic=60798.msg566149#msg566149" class="bbc_link new_win" target="_blank">http://www.goddessfantasy.net/bbs/?topic=60798.msg566149#msg566149</a><br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i>原文</i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">Wisdom in the Flesh<br>Source Ultimate Campaign pg. 64, Legacy of Fire Player&#039;s Guide pg. 9, Advanced Player&#039;s Guide pg. 1<br>Category Religion<br>Requirement(s) Irori<br>Your hours of meditation on inner perfection and the nature of strength and speed allow you to focus your thoughts to achieve things your body might not normally be able to do on its own. Select any Strength-, Constitution-, or Dexterity-based skill. You may make checks with that skill using your Wisdom modifier instead of the skill’s normal ability score. That skill is always a class skill for you.</div></div></div><br><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size"><strong>屠亡使（Undead Slayer）</strong></span><br>出自《Ultimate Campaign pg. 64, Advanced Player&#039;s Guide pg. 1》<br>类型：宗教<br>需求：法莱斯玛<br>信仰的核心教条从幼时起就在影响你，你将不死生物视为必须消灭的可憎秽物，这样他们的灵魂才能够前往彼方接受审判。你对不死生物的武器伤害获得+1背景加值。<br><a href="http://www.goddessfantasy.net/bbs/index.php?topic=59876.msg556552#msg556552" class="bbc_link new_win" target="_blank">http://www.goddessfantasy.net/bbs/index.php?topic=59876.msg556552#msg556552</a><br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">Undead Slayer (Pharasma)<br>Source Ultimate Campaign pg. 64, Advanced Player&#039;s Guide pg. 1<br>Category Religion<br>Requirement(s) Pharasma<br>Instructed at a young age in the tenets of the faith of Pharasma, you view the undead as abominations that must be destroyed so their souls can journey beyond to be judged. You gain a +1 trait bonus on weapon damage rolls against undead.</div></div></div></div>
