<div class="inner" id="msg_1033149"><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size"><strong>【Varisia, Birthplace of Legends】</strong></span><br><br><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size"><strong>瓦瑞西亚刺青（Varisian Tattoo）</strong></span><br>出自《瓦瑞西亚，传说摇篮 pg. 19》<br>类型：种族<br>需求：人类——瓦瑞西亚人<br>你身负你的族人为你精心制作的纹身，标示着你是道路上的自由子女（free son or daughter of the road）。你在对抗魅惑和胁迫效果的豁免获得+1背景加值。此外，你擅长使用刃巾（bladed scarf）和星刃（starknife）。<br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i>原文</i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">Varisian Tattoo<br>Source Varisia, Birthplace of Legends pg. 8<br>Category Race<br>Requirement(s) Human - Varisian<br>You bear the elaborate tattoos of your people, marking you as a free son or daughter of the road. You gain a +1 trait bonus on saving throws against charm and compulsion effects. Additionally, you are proficient with bladed scarves and starknives.</div></div></div><br><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size"><strong>休盎提纹身（Shoanti Tattoo）</strong></span><br>出自《瓦瑞西亚，传说诞生之地 pg. 6》<br>类型：种族<br>需求：人类——休盎提人<br>在你成年时，你获得一个部落纹身，标记着你的部族和精魂图腾（查看内页以参考休盎提纹身的建议和设计）。你面对恐惧效果时获得+1背景加值。此外，你擅长使用裂地锤（earth breaker）、喀拉尔（Klar）和休盎提套牛绳（Bolas）。<br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i>原文</i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">Shoanti Tattoo<br>Source Varisia, Birthplace of Legends pg. 6 (Amazon)<br>Category Race<br>Requirement(s) Human - Shoanti<br>Upon reaching adulthood, you received a tribal tattoo, marking you with the symbols of your quah and totem spirits (see the inside back cover for suggestions and designs for Shoanti tattoos). You gain a +1 trait bonus on saving throws against fear effects. Additionally, you are proficient with earth breakers, klars, and Shoanti bolas.</div></div></div><br><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size"><strong>休盎提骏马（Shoanti Steed）</strong></span><br>出自《瓦瑞西亚，传说诞生之地 pg. 6》<br>类型：种族<br>需求：人类——休盎提人<br>你的游牧文化给予你深刻的了解和尊重漫游在你家园的马匹。你在开始游戏时获得一只已战斗训练的轻型马（Pathfinder RPG Bestiary 177）。当你无鞍骑乘这匹马时，视你为有骑乘鞍座下骑乘（为马装备任何鞍座都会失去此好处）。除了最恶劣的环境之外，这匹马可以在定居点外自力更生。如果在社区以外吹口哨，马通常在1d6分钟内到达。如果你的马被杀，你可以通过返回你的氏族并为它的灵魂守夜，从而获得一匹新的马（仪式中须要用上罕见的香草和焚香，价值100gp）。<br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i>原文</i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">Shoanti Steed<br>Source Varisia, Birthplace of Legends pg. 6<br>Category Race<br>Requirement(s) Human - Shoanti<br>Your nomadic culture gives you a profound knowledge of and respect for the horses that roam your homelands. You begin play with a combat trained light horse (Pathfinder RPG Bestiary 177). While riding this horse bareback, you are treated as though you were riding it with a riding saddle (placing any actual saddle upon the horse negates this benefit). The horse can fend for itself outside of settlements in all but the most hostile environments. If whistled for outside of a community, the horse typically arrives within 1d6 minutes. If your horse is slain, you may receive a new horse by returning to your clan and performing a vigil for its spirit (a rite that costs 100 gp in rare herbs and incense).</div></div></div><br><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size"><strong>哈罗命定（Harrow Chosen）</strong></span><br>出自《瓦瑞西亚，传说诞生之地 pg. 8》<br>类型：种族<br>需求：人类——瓦瑞西亚人<br>你的一生都与你家族的哈罗卡组有着神秘的联系。你带着你家祖传的哈罗卡组开始游戏。如果你使用这一副特殊的哈罗卡组作为施放预言法术的额外法器成分，你的施法者等级被视为高2级。另外，每周两次，你可以花费十分钟用特殊的动作向哈罗卡组问卜，以获得如与你角色等级相同的施法者的法术占卜术（augury）的效果。除你之外，其他人都无法从这副哈罗卡组中获得这些收益。如果你的哈罗卡组损坏，你无法替换它。但是，你可以通过回到你的家族，花费300gp购买材料，并且花费一周沉浸于你族人的歌声和故事中，以此创造一幅新的哈罗卡组，获得遗失的家传卡组一半的收益。<br><a href="http://www.goddessfantasy.net/bbs/index.php?topic=83830.msg830952#msg830952" class="bbc_link new_win" target="_blank">http://www.goddessfantasy.net/bbs/index.php?topic=83830.msg830952#msg830952</a><br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i>原文</i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">Harrow Chosen<br>Source Varisia, Birthplace of Legends pg. 8<br>Category Race<br>Requirement(s) Human - Varisian<br>All your life you’ve been drawn to the mysteries surrounding your family’s harrow deck. You begin play with your family’s heirloom harrow deck. If you use this specific harrow deck as an additional focus component when you cast a divination spell, your caster level is treated as being 2 levels higher. Additionally, twice per week, you can spend 10 minutes consulting this harrow deck on a particular action to gain the effects of the spell augury as a spellcaster of your character level. No one other than you gains these benefits from this harrow deck. If your harrow deck is destroyed, it cannot be replaced. However, by returning to your family, paying 300 gp on materials, and spending 1 week immersed in the songs and stories of your people, you can create a new harrow deck that grants half the benefits of the lost heirloom.</div></div></div><br><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size"><strong>雪花弃儿（Alabaster Outcast）</strong></span><br>出自《瓦瑞西亚，传说摇篮 pg. 30，破碎虚星玩家手册 pg. 4》<br>类型：战役<br>需求：破碎虚星<br>你是伟迹城最富有的家庭中的一员……或者更确切地说，你曾经是。一场阴谋让你失去了所有权利，还被剥夺了继承权。现在，你希望远离城市去创造财富，为了去羞辱你以前的仇人，你加入了开拓者协会。尽管你流亡在外，你的名字仍然在伟迹城里有相当大的分量，你在城里时，交涉和恐吓上获得了+1的背景加值，另外，你开始获得一套贵族服装、一个图章戒指和一个额外的而价值不超过200gp的非魔法物品。<br>你的姓可能狄瑞克斯、凯筠、曼都瑞安、尼若登、斯盖勒丁、沃尔德马、温德奥迪或沃什特（但可能你的选择是另一个；查看开拓者战役设定：伟迹城——纪念碑市）。<br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i>原文</i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">Alabaster Outcast<br>Source Varisia, Birthplace of Legends pg. 30 (Amazon), Shattered Star Player&#039;s Guide pg. 4<br>Category Campaign<br>Requirement(s) Shattered Star<br>You are a member of one of Magnimar’s wealthiest families… or rather, you used to be. A falling-out left you disowned and disinherited. Now you hope to get away from the city and find fortune enough to shame your former kinsfolk—goals which led you to the Pathfinder Society. Despite your exile, your name still carries considerable weight in Magnimar, and you gain a +1 trait bonus on Diplomacy and Intimidate checks made within the city. Additionally, you start play with a noble’s outfit, a signet ring, and a single additional nonmagical item worth no more than 200 gp. Your last name is probably Derexhi, Kaddren, Mindurian, Niroden, Scarnetti, Valdemar, Vanderale, or Versade (but may be another of your choosing; see Magnimar, City of Monuments).</div></div></div></div>
