<div class="inner" id="msg_1046228"><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size"><strong>【Weapon Master&#039;s Handbook】</strong></span><br><br><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size"><strong>武僧武器技巧（Monk Weapon Skill）</strong></span><br>出自《武器大师手册 pg. 5》<br>类型：战斗<br>在完美学社（Houses of Perfection）的学习让你的武僧武器攻击更加致命。选择一个你擅长的武僧武器（徒手攻击不满足这个要求）。当使用这个武器时你在伤害上获得+1背景加值。<br><a href="http://www.goddessfantasy.net/bbs/index.php?topic=91437.msg876921#msg876921" class="bbc_link new_win" target="_blank">http://www.goddessfantasy.net/bbs/index.php?topic=91437.msg876921#msg876921</a><br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i>原文</i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">Monk Weapon Skill<br>Source Weapon Master&#039;s Handbook pg. 5<br>Category Basic (Combat)<br>Your exposure to teaching from the Houses of Perfection makes your attacks with monk weapons even more deadly. Select one monk weapon with which you are proficient (unarmed attacks do not qualify for this purpose). You gain a +1 trait bonus on damage rolls with this weapon.</div></div></div><br><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size"><strong>游猎射程（Roving Range）</strong></span><br>出自《武器大师手册 pg. 5》<br>类型：战斗<br>你从海盗那学会在接近目标的同时充分利用远程攻击。你持用的远程武器（投掷武器除外）的射程增量增加5尺。<br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i>原文</i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">Roving Range<br>Source Weapon Master&#039;s Handbook pg. 5<br>Category Basic (Combat)<br>You learned from pirates to make the most of ranged attacks as you close with targets. Increase the range increment of ranged weapons (but not thrown weapons) you wield by 5 feet.</div></div></div><br><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size"><strong>奥多里心眼（Aldori Caution）</strong></span><br>出自《武器大师手册 pg. 4》<br>类型：战斗<br>你从奥多里的教练那学会防守性动作。当你进行防御式战斗或是全防御动作时，你的AC额外获得+1闪避加值。<br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i>原文</i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">Aldori Caution<br>Source Weapon Master&#039;s Handbook pg. 4<br>Category Basic (Combat)<br>You learned defensive moves from Aldori trainers. You gain an additional +1 dodge bonus to Armor Class while you fight defensively or use the total defense action.</div></div></div></div>
